@startuml
title Diagrama de Secuencia - Crear Programa
actor "Administrador" as Admin
participant "Frontend (React)" as FE
participant "API (FastAPI)" as API
participant "ProgramaService" as Service
participant "ProgramaRepository" as Repo
database "Base de Datos" as DB
Admin -> FE: Clic en "Nuevo Programa"
activate FE
FE --> Admin: Mostrar Formulario
Admin -> FE: Ingresa nombre del programa y Guardar
FE -> API: POST /programas (ProgramaCreate JSON)
activate API
API -> Service: crear_programa(programa_create)
activate Service
Service -> Repo: create(programa_model)
activate Repo
Repo -> DB: INSERT INTO programas ...
activate DB
DB --> Repo: ID nuevo programa
deactivate DB
Repo --> Service: Programa (con ID)
deactivate Repo
Service --> API: ProgramaResponse
deactivate Service
API --> FE: 201 Created (Programa JSON)
deactivate API
FE -> FE: Actualizar Lista / Notificar Éxito
FE --> Admin: Mostrar "Programa creado correctamente"
deactivate FE
@enduml
